profile.bio: I am an alumni of Walsh Jesuit High School and The Ohio State University where I was the VP and co-founder of the Open Source Software Club.  Professionally I have worked for HP, Starbak Communications, Alcara PLS, Mobile Armor, Exegy, and now Tumblr.
